{"tid":1448664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:16:52.000Z","uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0be1946c1ec2f8e49cbd84be1285d0c90613bff","tid":1448664,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=a49e1ac4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel:&amp;nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=7fa5f789\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"629554a594f194aef768f2cf80ab99021b2a148b","tid":1448664,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6071765432992f46f1dac887bc7e16100bff53","tid":1448664,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0cbf94424ee4e60ca73fcaa7f6ea5074e925df","tid":1448664,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d657af681ccb3ec2ac21ef3d3141b72a25dfae7","tid":1448664,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike